<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />There our captors required songs from us,</para>

<para style="q1">and those who mocked us required us to be happy, saying,</para>

<para style="q1">"Sing us one of the songs of Zion."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />How could we sing a song about Yahweh</para>

<para style="q1">in a foreign land?</para>
